1912 Guelph Maple Leafs Roster

1912 Guelph Maple Leafs Statistics

The Guelph Maple Leafs of the Canadian League ended the 1912 season with a record of 39 wins and 51 losses, finishing seventh in the CL.

George Needham and Fred Applegate served as manager.
